file_content.text: Come on, cough it up. Every name, every date, every blasted key.
I don't--I don't have, I don't know what you're talking about.
The cattle run the slaughterhouse now, partner. Don't play dumb.
Oh. That prisoner list. Of course. Right here.
While you're in there, mind telling me what became of a group called "the Circle"?
Excuse me, folks.
Yeah. I know them. Ran off into one of the vaults. Y'know the big things that all the scary stuff comes out of.
Setting up some kind of hub out there. I don't know what.
Now if you don't mind, we owe this guy a beating.
Beat him and I kill you.
Don't you dare.
Uh, right, looks like you get off easy this time. We'll--we'll just be going.
Be my guest.
Thank you, Sith.
If that sort of thing pleases you.
I don't care.
It most certainly does. Thank you, Sith.
Now if you don't mind, we got a lesson in mind for this guy.
We don't mind, do we?
Of course we do! Kill them! Kill them all!
I think you'd all look better dead.
Actually.... [Kill everyone.]
Aggghhh!
I'll be taking that list.
Give it to me.
Um, right, sorry, Sith. You want the list, it's yours. We'll just be... we'll just be going.
Take your hands off that man. I need him and his prisoner list.
Release him.
Sith, uh, sorry, Lord Sith. We didn't mean nothing. We didn't know this was your guy.
Yeah, we'll be getting out of your way. Don't hurt us, please.
Don't know why you bothered. You're just going to kill me like all the others, aren't you?
If you tell me what I want to know, I might consider freeing you.
Not necessarily.
Sorry if I don't fall on my knees in gratitude.
In spite of my outward appearance, I'm really not such a bad person.
I don't want to kill anyone.
The day I believe that about a Sith is the day I become one.
I don't know what you're talking about.
Others?
Last I checked, it was your Empire that opened all the cages. Let freaks like them out.
I just hope my family made it out of here alive. But you don't care, do you?
What is it you want anyway?
A group called the Circle.
Tech savants. Criminals.
The Circle. I'm told they know a thing or two about strange tech.
A group of Nikto.
There's a group of Nikto with an inordinate love of technology.
The Circle.
Yeah, I remember them. Ran off into one of those big vaults a few days ago to do whatever it is they do.
Don't know if they're still alive, though.
Do yourself a favor and leave this planet.
Get to safety.
You don't have to tell me.
If you're wrong about this, I will kill you.
You'd better be right.
Like I'm going to stick around for that.
I'm getting the first shuttle out of here, if I have to steal it.
Thank you. [Kill him.]
Aggghhh!
